{"tid":1526263,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人一定會輸 , 而且會輸得好慘。","createTime":"2019-09-01T05:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T05:15:21.000Z","uid":292788,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"358b49c7d6012ea877e549d4d5d1914b0c96e9c5","tid":1526263,"uid":292788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:05:22.000Z","msg":"因為太多港人有良知，特別係新一代。<br />\n你地對住一個精神病病人講制度？　講理性討論？　講邏輯 ? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你地一定係傻撚左</span>，當年文革死左四千萬人。而家都仲執緊政。<br />\n<br />\n以下係歷史：<br />\n一九五七年四月三十日，毛澤東向全國保證：「言者無罪，聞者足戒。」但是，同年六月，他就發動反右派鬥爭，因言獲罪者，達一百萬。<br />\n<br />\n一九七八年十一月二十六日，鄧小平告訴日本民主社會黨委員長佐佐木良：「寫大字報是我國憲法允許的。群眾的議論不可怕。」但是，幾個月之後，群眾議論領袖魏京生、傅月華、劉青、任畹町等，紛紛被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">邪惡既人好清楚善良既人諗乜，但善良既人永遠唔會明。</span>"},{"pid":"2105012d99d50115bf8e6db9d52ffb4fc237a295","tid":1526263,"uid":177336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"901 機場攻略<br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span>到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到<span style=\"color: red;\">有隊就排</span>；利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：<span style=\"color: red;\">以巴士為優先</span>，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2Xy%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=ea3f5b9d\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXKf68.jpg&h=74d57433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxaV7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAxaV7a.jpg&h=13c2eb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZAnNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotZAnNa.jpg&h=f10fa124&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e4c12d2bbabbe06fdb1396dd5888cc80a773a6a","tid":1526263,"uid":228589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:08:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bc223745eadd417c80f447572f2ddebef38b5ae","tid":1526263,"uid":292788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e4c12d2bbabbe06fdb1396dd5888cc80a773a6a","tid":1526263,"uid":228589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:08:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:10:16.000Z","msg":"請自行思考"},{"pid":"f1e8b0b8311519daf530f7e84a2d1eea801789ac","tid":1526263,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:15:21.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QG5GZ57.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQG5GZ57.gif&h=70f70c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQ6rr7H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQ6rr7H.gif&h=2e882f27&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}